== ORCONF 2014 ==

The third annual project meeting is likely to be held in '''Munich, Germany''', and is tentatively scheduled to take place over the weekend of '''Saturday, October 11''' and '''Sunday, October 12'''.

More information on this event will be made available here and on the [[OR1K:Community_Portal#Mailing_lists|OpenRISC mailing lists]] over the coming months.
